					<hr />
					<div style="margin: 0 5ex;">Hi, how can I get a copy of the original Bitcoin rar distributed Fri, 09 Jan 2009?<br /><br />Originally this was posted at:<br /><br />http://downloads.sourceforge.net/bitcoin/bitcoin-0.1.0.rar<br /><br />This link is no longer valid.</div>
